text: Assa, ieell awen wayen imaanen. Ieell awen lqut n wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, - ieell asen lqut nnwen -; tilawin tieuoiyin iumnen, tilawin tieuoiyin seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, uqbel nnwen, ma tefkam asent tuccit nnsent; d uwqimen macci d ucmiten, ur teppeddum d temddukwal. Win iugin liman, mean igiten is. Neppa, di laxeot, seg imexsuoen
